Figure 3: 
A graphical representation of the predicted and validated human leukocyte antigen (HLA) binding of 119 selected SARS‐derived peptides binding to eight different HLA molecules. It illustrates combinations that were (A) predicted and confirmed binders (true positives, ▪); (B) predicted, but not confirmed, binders (false positives,
); (C) predicted, but not confirmed, non‐binders (false negatives,
); and (D) predicted and confirmed non‐binders (true negatives, □).
